# <type>[optional scope]: <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# Type can be:
#   feat     (new feature)
#   fix      (bug fix)
#   docs     (documentation)
#   style    (formatting, missing semi colons, etc; no code change)
#   refactor (refactoring production code)
#   test     (adding tests, refactoring test; no production code change)
#   chore    (updating build tasks, package manager configs; no production code change)
#   perf     (performance improvements)
#   ci       (continuous integration changes)
#   build    (build system or external dependencies)
#   revert   (reverting a previous commit)
#
# Scope examples:
#   api, auth, config, domain, infra, security, tests
#
# Examples:
#   feat(api): add environmental impact calculation endpoint
#   fix(auth): resolve API key validation issue
#   docs: update installation instructions
#   refactor(domain): extract calculation service from controller
#   test(api): add integration tests for webhook signature verification
#   chore(deps): update FastAPI to v0.104.0